{"tid":1580301,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"唔該 以後有人出事， 第一時間唔好諗點解嗰個人會出事，唔好blame the victims","createTime":"2019-09-19T04:06:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T13:49:24.000Z","uid":135867,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"321a24630ed2222afaedc2cd2706e07caf30acc4","tid":1580301,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:06:22.000Z","msg":"畀人打/騷擾已經係好慘<br />\n上到嚟開個post仲要畀你班連登仔 問點解當時唔做乜乜乜呀<br />\n點解要著成咁呀<br />\n點解唔搵人陪呀<br />\n點解唔打返轉頭呀<br />\n點解唔搵記者呀<br />\n點解唔報警呀<br />\n<br />\n其實有好多時都係突發當下未必一定諗到點做<br />\n可能上嚟開po只係想提高大家警覺性<br />\n我哋要諗嘅係點樣去減少呢類事情發生<br />\n而唔係怪嗰個人<br />\n<br />\n件事已經發生咗要諗嘅係解決方法同埋避免 同類事情發生"},{"pid":"e35c9921ababb486328130e532262a41d0307ae1","tid":1580301,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:07:09.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[公海 文宣 行動整合] 9.29全球抗赤納粹集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1579667\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1579667</a><br />\n全世界一齊對準ChiNazi極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BZiskWr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBZiskWr.png&h=b85bf973&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">9.29 Global AntiChiNazi 文宣、資訊、行動整合Channel</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/AntiChinazi929\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FAntiChinazi929&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5V8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=56c3883b\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/AntiChinazi929</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>9.29 Global AntiChiNazi 公海</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5V8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=6317c55d\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ</a>"},{"pid":"b75d235cbeb24738732508bc11da8a46bf4b1e01","tid":1580301,"uid":42194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:13:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WnLxWAc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWnLxWAc.jpg&h=5ea06781&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w2Leqwm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw2Leqwm.jpg&h=6f74c0e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日期： 9月21日 時間：2:00集合，3點起步<br />\n路線：新和里  -&gt; 屯門政府合署<br />\n<br />\n屯門公園<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">(一)禁打賞</span><br />\n 要求修改《遊樂場地規例》，禁止一切在公園範圍內涉及任何形式金錢之打賞，行乞，捐贈行為<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">(二)投訴權</span><br />\n 呼籲立法會民政事務委員會各委員正視民意，盡快修訂《遊樂場地規》使附近街坊同樣擁有投訴權利<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">(三)加強執法</span><br />\n 要求康文署增加合資格執法人員及簡化檢控程序，加強執法及檢控違法行為<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(四)正視設施不足</span><br />\n 要求康文署及屯門區議會，正視區內老人文娛設施不足問題<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">(五)檢討管理</span><br />\n 要求康文署檢討屯門公園及割下公共空間的管理，有效分配公園及其他公共空間的使用權<br />\n<br />\n交通：<br />\n巴士： <br />\n58M / 58X / 63X / 260X / 960 - 紅橋站落車<br />\n黨鐵：<br />\n1. 西鐵兆康站落車<br />\n2. 轉乘輕鐵 751 (往友愛）或610 （往屯門碼頭）"},{"pid":"bccf5a35f84c6083b6444ea27f671d113bbad2f8","tid":1580301,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:15:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf3cb83f1a446c660a25f77f5cbc5a0df5f227cd","tid":1580301,"uid":52705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:19:22.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"965f2c7d228828b5427ca23deab2a6887a8b4fd0","tid":1580301,"uid":231909